author: The Current
title: Mary Lucia reflects on being a part of The Current for 17 years.

author: The Current
description:
Mark Wheat, the first ever DJ hired by The Current, talks about the emphasis the station had on local music since day one. 

We’re having a party on-air and you’re invited! Share your favorite memory of The Current and we will share on-air on January 24.
